Blackouts or load-shedding has been in effect for fifteen years now. And there's no end in sight to the problems that plague Eskom. For more, #eNCA speaks to Energy Analyst, Sampson Mamphweli. Courtesy #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Stage 8 rolling blackouts can't be ruled out, according to energy analyst, Sampson Mamphweli. He says the grid is very unstable and the utility is waiting for diesel supplies. Eskom has ramped up power cuts to Stage 4 this weekend between 8am and 10pm. Watch the video above for more details.